summaries.short: Jakub breaks up with Marketa. Zuzana and Milan agree to a separation. Ema finally realizes the depth of Karel's feelings for her.
summaries.full: Jakub breaks up with Marketa. Zuzana and Milan agree to a separation. Ema finally realizes the depth of Karel's feelings for her and the two await the birth of her baby. Sarka and Jakub finally get together.

summaries.short: Season Two Premiere. Sarka and Jakub look for an apartment together and hope to start a family.
summaries.full: Season Two Premiere. Sarka and Jakub look for an apartment together and hope to start a family. Ema and Karel are happy parenting their six-month-old, Berta, but exhausted. Milan, now divorced from Zuzana, drives a cab and picks up a familiar customer. And Zuzana finds herself lonely while her son studies abroad.

summaries.short: Zuzana comes out to Milan and tells him she wants a divorce. Ema tells Karel that she's pregnant with Milan's baby, and doesn't tell Milan.
summaries.full: Zuzana comes out to Milan and tells him she wants a divorce. Ema tells Karel that she's pregnant with Milan's baby, and doesn't tell Milan. Marketa has a miscarriage. Sarka gets hustled out of her savings.
